        "context_sentences",
        [
          10
        ]
      ],
      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "Skx-jEBr5B",
      "rebuttal_id": "Hyl3QZqMjS",
      "sentence_index": 24,
      "text": "We first transform a signal into frequency domain and keep 2N+1 components with the lowest frequencies: f(-N), \u2026 , f(0), \u2026 ,f(N).",
