      "coarse": "concur",
      "fine": "rebuttal_answer",
      "alignment": [
        "context_sentences",
        [
          10
        ]
      ],
      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "Skx-jEBr5B",
      "rebuttal_id": "Hyl3QZqMjS",
      "sentence_index": 26,
      "text": "In this case, the imaginary part in time domain is zero because of symmetry.",
      "suffix": "",
      "coarse": "concur",
      "fine": "rebuttal_answer",
      "alignment": [
        "context_sentences",
        [
          10
        ]
      ],
      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "Skx-jEBr5B",
      "rebuttal_id": "Hyl3QZqMjS",
      "sentence_index": 27,
      "text": "Now, suppose the output size is 2N+2: f(-N), \u2026 , f(0),",
      "suffix": "",
      "coarse": "concur",
      "fine": "rebuttal_answer",
      "alignment": [
        "context_sentences",
        [
          10
        ]
      ],
      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "Skx-jEBr5B",
      "rebuttal_id": "Hyl3QZqMjS",
      "sentence_index": 28,
      "text": "\u2026 f(N), f(N+1)",
      "suffix": "",
      "coarse": "concur",
      "fine": "rebuttal_answer",
      "alignment": [
        "context_sentences",
        [
          10
        ]
      ],
      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "Skx-jEBr5B",
      "rebuttal_id": "Hyl3QZqMjS",
      "sentence_index": 29,
      "text": ".",
      "suffix": "",
      "coarse": "concur",
      "fine": "rebuttal_answer",
      "alignment": [
        "context_sentences",
        [
          10
        ]
      ],
      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "Skx-jEBr5B",
      "rebuttal_id": "Hyl3QZqMjS",
      "sentence_index": 30,
      "text": "In this case, the imaginary part is not zero.",
      "suffix": "",
      "coarse": "concur",
      "fine": "rebuttal_answer",
      "alignment": [
        "context_sentences",
        [
          10
        ]
      ],
      "details": {}
    },
    {
      "review_id": "Skx-jEBr5B",
      "rebuttal_id": "Hyl3QZqMjS",
      "sentence_index": 31,
      "text": "However, if we set f(N+1) to 0, it imaginary part becomes zero again.",
